OL,3,CWheelchair user killed after car
OL,4,Cploughs into pedestrians
OL,6,FA driver has been arrested after a car
OL,7,Fploughed into pedestrians in Bradford,
OL,8,Fkilling a wheelchair user.
OL,10,FThe 50-year-old victim was in a
OL,11,Fpedestrianised area of Market Street,
OL,12,Fnear a branch of Barclays, when a blue
OL,13,FNissan Qashqai mounted the kerb and
OL,14,Fhit him at 3.22pm on Sunday. He died
OL,15,Fat the scene.
OL,17,FA 31-year-old-man who was also hit
OL,18,Fsuffered serious head injuries. A 13-
OL,19,Fyear-old boy suffered minor injuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
