CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1784116090
OL,3,CWheelchair user killed after car
OL,4,Cploughs into pedestrians
OL,6,FA 30-year-old Bradford man was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of causing death
OL,8,Fby dangerous driving and other traffic
OL,9,Foffences.
OL,11,FHe was interviewed before being
OL,12,Freleased on police bail pending
OL,13,Fenquiries, West Yorkshire Police said.
OL,15,FDet Sgt Nina Roper, of the Major
OL,16,FCollision Enquiry Team, said:
OL,17,F"Multiple enquiries remain ongoing
OL,18,Finto this very serious incident, which
OL,19,Fhas sadly resulted in a man losing his
OL,20,Flife and another man suffering serious
OL,21,Finjuries.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
