OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F336A1784116090
OL,3,CWheelchair user killed after car
OL,4,Cploughs into pedestrians
OL,6,F"We are investigating the exact
OL,7,Fcircumstances of the collision,
OL,8,Fincluding why the Nissan mounted the
OL,9,Fkerb, and would like to speak to
OL,10,Fanyone who saw or has footage of what
OL,11,Fhappened or of the Nissan beforehand."
